Another ModENCODE mess... From the sample name (GSM509821: Head_Dmel_Female (GA II)) it is likely Illumina GAII, so SRA wrong and no change made. See https://github.com/BgeeDB/expression-annotations/issues/98#issuecomment-168948504, https://github.com/BgeeDB/expression-annotations/issues/98#issuecomment-168949518, and https://github.com/BgeeDB/expression-annotations/issues/98#issuecomment-170598340
